    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以沙漠边陲的小镇“潮痕镇”为中心，为了寻找在一次神秘的事件中消失无踪的勘探队所留下的谜团，游戏的故事将会逐渐展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/d51248da33ad49cb488553e8b1f92854.poster.avif?t=1757647184\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/d51248da33ad49cb488553e8b1f92854.webm?t=1757647184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/d51248da33ad49cb488553e8b1f92854.mp4?t=1757647184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拿上你的提灯</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/0a21eebf12041c5ef13b072f87288710.poster.avif?t=1757647184\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/0a21eebf12041c5ef13b072f87288710.webm?t=1757647184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/0a21eebf12041c5ef13b072f87288710.mp4?t=1757647184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为勘探队最重要的配备，你的提灯不仅是应对威胁的武器，还具有多种用途</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在击破敌人的同时，探索其与不同的元素交互的方式</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索独特场景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/5171eb6adb2e03fef318aa6a8c0b6848.poster.avif?t=1757647184\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/5171eb6adb2e03fef318aa6a8c0b6848.webm?t=1757647184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/5171eb6adb2e03fef318aa6a8c0b6848.mp4?t=1757647184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在潮痕镇区域宏大而风格迥异，并隐含多种秘密的场景中沉浸探索</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭开谜团</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/400161c503cd356fd85c8edd63a13975.poster.avif?t=1757647184\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/400161c503cd356fd85c8edd63a13975.webm?t=1757647184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319620/extras/400161c503cd356fd85c8edd63a13975.mp4?t=1757647184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助奇异的“车厢”在潮痕镇的时空中穿行，逐渐揭开隐藏的谜团</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着谜团的逐渐揭示，关于事件的真相以及新的可能性也会展现在你的眼前</p>",
